            https://github.com/material-components/material-components-android/issues/1955#issuecomment-752143062
        -->
        <item name="materialCalendarTheme">@style/ColorsTheme.MaterialCalendarTheme</item>
        <item name="materialTimePickerTheme">@style/ColorsTheme.MaterialTimePickerTheme</item>
